=== SUPERSEDED 2026-05-22 ===
This smoke was never run. The bash approach it describes — overseer-on-stop.sh
reconstructing the last assistant message from the transcript JSONL — was
abandoned: the transcript is flushed asynchronously, so a Stop hook races the
writer and reads a stale/empty turn (anthropics/claude-code#15813).

The replacement, .claude/hooks/overseer_stop.py, reads the last assistant
message from the `last_assistant_message` field Claude Code now ships directly
on the Stop envelope (field probe PASS, /tmp/field-probe.log, 2026-05-22).

overseer-on-stop.sh, _stop_probe.sh, _field_probe.sh and
tests/test_overseer_on_stop_hook.py were deleted in the same change.

The new design and the new post-restart smoke procedure live in
artifacts/spikes/auto-overseer-redesign-2026-05-22.md.
